  "id": "crescent",
  "name": "Crescent",
  "title": "Fledgling Shadow",
  "description": "\"Bad boy, Crescent! Bad! Bad!\"\n\n\"Kyuu...\"\n\n\"What'd the dragon do this time?\"\n\n\"I hope you didn't want dinner tonight, Solas, because our eggs have vanished.\"\n\n\"What do you mean? Did they roll out of your basket again?\"\n\n\"Of course not! I was just putting the pepper on my omelette when Crescent sneezed on it, or something. This black stuff came out of his mouth instead of fire --\"\n\n\"Black stuff? Like tar?\"\n\n\"No, like a shadow. Or a bit of night. I don't know. Anyway, it hit the eggs and made them disappear, so Crescent's not getting any more grapes for a week. Hmph.\"\n\n\"Kyuu...\"",
